OL,3,CParking industry leader: 'If the signs
OL,4,Care unclear, park somewhere else'
OL,6,FPrivate parking companies "don't want
OL,7,Fto issue parking charges", an industry
OL,8,Fleader has insisted, despite around
OL,9,F41,000 tickets being handed out in
OL,10,FBritain each day.
OL,12,FWill Hurley, chief executive of trade
OL,13,Fbody the International Parking
OL,14,FCommunity (IPC), said operators want
OL,15,Fdrivers to park "where they need to,
OL,16,Fwhen they need to" without breaking
OL,17,Fany rules.
