OL,6,F"If you're thinking about it, just
OL,7,Fdon't park in a way that gets a
OL,8,Fparking charge," he said. "If you're
OL,9,Freally that upset by it, just follow
OL,10,Fthe signs."
OL,12,F"If the signs are unclear, go and park
OL,13,Fsomewhere else."
OL,15,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, Mr
OL,16,FHurley insisted: "Parking operators
OL,17,Fdon't want to issue charges. They want
OL,18,Fpeople to park where they need to,
OL,19,Fwhen they need to."
