OL,6,FThey issue parking charge notices
OL,7,F(PCNs) ` which are invoices or demands
OL,8,Ffor money ` when they claim someone
OL,9,Fhas breached the land owner's rules,
OL,10,Ffor example not entering their
OL,11,Fregistration correctly into a machine,
OL,12,Foverstaying or not parking within a
OL,13,Fbay.
OL,15,FEach ticket can be up to #100, with a
OL,16,Fminimum discount of 40% if paid within
OL,17,F14 days.
