OL,6,F"Any business is there to make money,"
OL,7,Fhe said. "But the reality is, the vast
OL,8,Fmajority of money that comes in in the
OL,9,Fparking industry comes from people
OL,10,Fpaying for parking."
OL,12,FThe RAC says it expects 14.5 million
OL,13,Fpenalty notices this year - a
OL,14,Fsignificant rise and amounting to #1.4
OL,15,Fbillion in fines.
OL,17,FThere are calls for a new independent
OL,18,Fwatchdog to ensure charges are fair
OL,19,Fand private parking companies in the
OL,20,FUK have promised to update their code
OL,21,Fof conduct.
